{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/WhatIsReforgedTD.png?t=1717612842\" /><br>Are you up for a tower defense with RPG elements, like a skill tree and a level system? Are you looking for a game with unique units that have individual abilities and are balanced according to the scissors-stone-paper principle? Then REFORGED TD might be just right for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Some information about the developers:</h2>Behind Reforged Tower Defense there is no big development studio like most games here on Steam. Reforged Tower Defense was developed by me alone.<br><br>If you have questions, feedback or technical problems with the game, feel free to contact me at any time. I will do my best to answer as soon as possible and offer assistance if necessary. I would also be happy to hear from you if you just had a good time with REFORGED TD. After all, this is the goal of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REFORGED Tower Defense offers you:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A genre mix of tower defense and RPG<br></li><li>An extensive skills tree<br></li><li>A range of unique abilities, towers and units<br></li><li>Scissors-stone-paper-principle, where each unit shows weaknesses and strengths.<br></li><li>Singleplayer and cooperative modes against bots of varying difficulties<br></li><li>Frequent content and feature updates</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1044110/extras/TheNightsSecretsShop.png?t=1717612842\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Firestorm","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1044110/2a0bef949839d80bf4f7e260cdb0cb6d0c64347e.jpg"},{"name":"Everybody starts out small","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1044110/34822cd4b64b3318ab8880d225be7dc8a4ae6ef7.jpg"},{"name":"The journey begins.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steams